              "raw": "{\n  \"farmer_id\": 4,\n  \"kg_received\": 30.500,\n  \"commodity_rate_fcfa\": 1000\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Records a commodity repayment for a farmer.\n\n**FIFO logic:**\n1. `total_credited = round(kg_received × commodity_rate_fcfa)` = 30 500 FCFA\n2. Applies to oldest open/partial debt first (Amenan's 72 000 FCFA)\n3. Debt becomes `partial` with 41 500 FCFA remaining\n4. Any surplus beyond all debts is silently discarded\n\nThe response includes `debts_affected` with the `amount_applied_fcfa` pivot value for each settled debt."
